articles.author: Etan Vlessing
articles.title: Rosie O’Donnell Has Moved to Ireland After Trump Election: “It Has Been Heartbreaking” - Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: “When you know it is safe for all citizens to have equal rights there in America, that’s when we will consider coming back,” the Emmy-winning star said on a TikTok video about a possible return.
articles.content:
Rosie O’Donnell has confirmed she has moved from the United States to Ireland, where she is in the process of taking up citizenship.
